  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Black_Ears\" title=\"Black Ears\"><img alt=\"Black Ears.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/50px-Black_Ears.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/75px-Black_Ears.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/100px-Black_Ears.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Cheyk</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Black_Ears\" title=\"Black Ears\"><img alt=\"Black Ears.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/50px-Black_Ears.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/75px-Black_Ears.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Black_Ears.svg/100px-Black_Ears.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Black_Ears\" title=\"Black Ears\">Black Ears</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Chella\" title=\"Chella\">Chella</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cheyk</b> is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Ears\" title=\"Black Ears\">Black Ears</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Chella\" title=\"Chella\">Chella</a> is the daughter of Cheyk,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> but Cheyk's gender and living status are unknown. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cheyk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122750\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.099 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.378 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 418/1000000\nPreprocessor